 473:src/engine.cpp ****     // Service the USB device stack from the audio callback (~12 kHz) at ~2 kHz, so
 474:src/engine.cpp ****     // the isochronous audio-IN endpoint is fed every USB frame â€” the control loop
 475:src/engine.cpp ****     // (~150 Hz) is far too slow and starves it (ring overruns â†’ decimated audio).
 476:src/engine.cpp ****     // Bonus: this runs the capture ring's consumer (pre_load) in the SAME context
 477:src/engine.cpp ****     // as its producer (usb_audio_push above), so the ring is race-free.
